In [62]:
from sklearn import svm
from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier
from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split, GridSearchCV, cross_val_score
In [60]:
X = np.array(df_train.drop(["Outcome"], 1))
y = np.array(df_train["Outcome"])
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(X, y, test_size = 0.15)
In [69]:
clf1 = KNeighborsClassifier(n_neighbors=3)
clf1.fit(X_train, y_train)
acc = clf1.score(X_test, y_test)
print(f"KNN: {acc}")

clf2 = svm.SVC(kernel="linear", C=3.0)
clf2.fit(X_train, y_train)
acc = clf2.score(X_test, y_test)
print(f"SVC: {acc}")

clf3 = DecisionTreeClassifier()
clf3.fit(X_train, y_train)
acc = clf3.score(X_test, y_test)
print(f"Decision Tree: {acc}")

clf4 = RandomForestClassifier()
clf4.fit(X_train, y_train)
acc = clf4.score(X_test, y_test)
print(f"Random Forest: {acc}")

KNN: 0.7327586206896551
SVC: 0.75
Decision Tree: 0.646551724137931
Random Forest: 0.7241379310344828
In [66]:
parameters = {
    "n_neighbors": (1,3,5,7,9,11,13,15),
    "weights": ("uniform", "distance"),
}

untuned_model = KNeighborsClassifier()
clf1 = GridSearchCV(untuned_model, parameters, cv=5)
clf1.fit(X_train, y_train)
acc = clf1.score(X_test, y_test)
print(f"KNN: {acc}")

KNN: 0.8017241379310345
